    <item>
      <title>欧洲股指期货因中国股市反弹停止而下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中国股市的全球性涨势暂停，欧洲股市将跟随亚洲股市的疲软走势下跌。由于对中东紧张局势升级的担忧，油价延续涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 22:36:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中东供应风险主导油价连续第三天上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-3</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价连续第三天上涨，因为交易商评估了中东的供应风险，预计以色列将在本周早些时候对伊朗发动导弹袭击后对伊朗进行报复性打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-3</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 22:16:20 GMT</pubDate>
